         <note id="AttachTheCableAsCloseAsPossibleToTh-801FA067"
               type="important"
               class="- topic/note ">Attach the cable as close as possible to the battery
poles, but above the battery connectors.</note>
         <p class="- topic/p ">To attach the BC5xx
measuring cable to the battery:</p>
